n efficient mechanism for\nstripping these atmospheres and transforming these planets into super Earths.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2022 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Jan 2023 08:30:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-01"}
