s are measured at very high\nfrequencies, which are not available for GW170817 but might be tested with next\ngeneration detectors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2022 18:00:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-22"}
