ro TES response to varying (AC)\nmagnetic fields. We quantify a worst-case TES responsivity to the applied AC\nmagnetic field of $\\sim10^5$ pA/G, and give a preliminary interpretation of the\npick-up mechanism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Jul 2022 04:48:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Jul 2022 02:54:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-01"}
