Our results\ncould provide some clues for the formation of Saturn's core as well as the\narchitecture of some exoplanetary systems with multiple cold giant planets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Jul 2022 08:09:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-31"}
